    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏介绍</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>这是一款基于VR的，有Roguelite元素的关卡制冒险射击游戏，<br></li><li>在游戏中，玩家扮演了一名在平行世界的埃及古墓中探险的冒险者，在巨大的地下世界中不断深入，为的是寻找传说中的秘宝。<br></li><li>地下世界的每一关都是随机生成的，玩家每一次失败后新的重启都是全新的体验。<br></li><li>在每次探险中，玩家可以找到各种不同的武器、以及有特殊能力的圣物道具。而不同武器和能力的组合将彻底改变游戏方式，带来独一无二的通关体验。</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2171010/extras/e70fb6519db3beaf675487d9f6d8818c.poster.avif?t=1709861547\" width=492 height=278 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2171010/extras/e70fb6519db3beaf675487d9f6d8818c.webm?t=1709861547\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2171010/extras/e70fb6519db3beaf675487d9f6d8818c.mp4?t=1709861547\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2171010/extras/e5927ecbfaeaba86e107158aea10f364.poster.avif?t=1709861547\" width=496 height=312 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2171010/extras/e5927ecbfaeaba86e107158aea10f364.webm?t=1709861547\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2171010/extras/e5927ecbfaeaba86e107158aea10f364.mp4?t=1709861547\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >多样的武器</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>经典的军用手枪，蝎式冲锋枪，短管霰弹枪等等。<br></li><li>疯狂的火焰喷射器，爆炸连弩，轻型仿燃料炮等等。<br></li><li>科幻的聚能电浆，奥坎镭射枪，重力枪等等。</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2171010/extras/8df288d56fd198faf1d0f6b75df293de.poster.avif?t=1709861547\" width=494 height=278 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2171010/extras/8df288d56fd198faf1d0f6b75df293de.webm?t=1709861547\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2171010/extras/8df288d56fd198faf1d0f6b75df293de.mp4?t=1709861547\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >强大的古老圣物</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>奥西里斯的面具 - 能够对攻击者施加死亡诅咒 。<br></li><li>荷鲁斯的护腕 - 能够造成瞬间的时间静止。<br></li><li>安卡的守护符 - 能够提供攻击回血能力。<br></li><li>元素戒指 - 能够对怪物造成冰冻、石化、灼伤等效果。<br></li><li>等等数十类。</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2171010/extras/86456f92d8d2571f64aa5acc05424667.poster.avif?t=1709861547\" width=496 height=312 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2171010/extras/86456f92d8d2571f64aa5acc05424667.webm?t=1709861547\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2171010/extras/86456f92d8d2571f64aa5acc05424667.mp4?t=1709861547\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >丰富的怪物类型</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>行动缓慢的木乃伊。<br></li><li>横冲直撞的墓地守卫。<br></li><li>成群结队的圣甲虫。<br></li><li>腐蚀大地的食人蝎。<br></li><li>巨大的阿努比斯雕像。<br></li><li>强大而可怕的法老幻影等等。</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >关卡</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2171010/extras/8bbafe5a55ad5926d1529ae0cb28c603.poster.avif?t=1709861547\" width=498 height=312 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2171010/extras/8bbafe5a55ad5926d1529ae0cb28c603.webm?t=1709861547\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2171010/extras/8bbafe5a55ad5926d1529ae0cb28c603.mp4?t=1709861547\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2171010/extras/1c3ef3b5d77cb3edbe54f8891a3162ea.poster.avif?t=1709861547\" width=496 height=312 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2171010/extras/1c3ef3b5d77cb3edbe54f8891a3162ea.webm?t=1709861547\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2171010/extras/1c3ef3b5d77cb3edbe54f8891a3162ea.mp4?t=1709861547\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2171010/extras/339eed9c7c9f0dd3e72fca89bebf8352.poster.avif?t=1709861547\" width=496 height=312 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2171010/extras/339eed9c7c9f0dd3e72fca89bebf8352.webm?t=1709861547\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2171010/extras/339eed9c7c9f0dd3e72fca89bebf8352.mp4?t=1709861547\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><a href=\"mailto:联系邮箱：special@xrlinkup.com\">联系邮箱：special@xrlinkup.com</a>",
